{
  "stem": "12904.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she waved to me and asked me to come further into the woods.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And she said, you know, I can't come to your house anymore, or you to mine.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "But we could meet here once in a while.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And I said, no, we couldn't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Because we would be found out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "Both of us would be in trouble.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "If we can't talk normally the way we used to, then we just can't see each other anymore.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And that was the last I heard of her.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "I went back by myself on the street car.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I guess she went on another street car home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And that was-- because I had had no Jewish friends-- I was the only Jewish girl in the class.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "Because I had no religious instruction, it was customary for the ministers, priests, and rabbis to come to the schools at the same time and give religious instruction to the students.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And since I didn't have any, I was allowed-- well, they told me to sit and do my homework while my Lutheran friends had their instruction.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Because I listened in on it, I didn't really do my homework.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "It would be a little hard to do that while somebody else is talking.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And so then, in 1933, I decided, since my friends, this friend and then this other friend I had had for about four years-- and we had been pretty close for those four years, too-- that I needed to have some Jewish friends.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And that's when I joined this German Jewish youth organization, which was very patriotic German.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We wanted to stay in Germany, actually.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "And we thought there would be a new Germany, and it would all change again.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was called Bund deutsch-judischer Jugend.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "That's a club of German Jewish youth.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
